replies.body:
If you're running Windows 10, this could be caused by the Windows Game Bar, which was updated recently to enable a feature called *Game DVR*. This feature has been causing system freezes for some players, so I recommend you disable the game bar entirely using [this guide.
](http://www.tenforums.com/tutorials/8637-game-bar-turn-off-windows-10-a.html)

Let me know if that helped.
